{
  "texts": [
    "To propel HMC research forward, Naseem et al.",
    "43 introduces the Reddit Health Mention Dataset (RHMD), a novel dataset derived from multi-domain Reddit data designed for HMC.",
    "RHMD comprises 10,015 manually labeled Reddit posts referencing 15 common disease or symptom terms, categorized into four labels: personal health mentions, non-personal health mentions, figurative health mentions, and hyperbolic health mentions.",
    "Leveraging RHMD, we propose HMCNET, a methodology that integrates target keyword identification (disease or symptom term) and user behavior hierarchically to enhance HMC.",
    "Experimental results showcase that our approach surpasses state-of-the-art methods, achieving an F1-Score of 0.75, marking an 11% improvement over existing methodologies."
  ]
}